7
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:53,000
05 Mori Calliope

8
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:08,000
Uncut Rock!!

9
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:49,000
[Song: Rivals and Equals]

10
00:03:49,700 --> 00:03:51,400
Base instincts take control

11
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,900
Like primal ways of a warrior

12
00:03:53,900 --> 00:03:56,300
Is it glory you're after, like me?

13
00:03:56,300 --> 00:03:58,700
Underestimated everywhere I turn

14
00:03:58,700 --> 00:04:01,100
Taking aim but it doesn't make a difference at all

15
00:04:01,100 --> 00:04:03,500
I got a million different enemies I cannot recall

16
00:04:03,500 --> 00:04:05,900
You're rocking up to a battle when you know that you'll fall

17
00:04:05,900 --> 00:04:08,300
Hidden motivation, watch it all burn

18
00:04:08,300 --> 00:04:10,500
I gotta tell you

19
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:12,800
I never liked you

20
00:04:12,800 --> 00:04:15,200
Now would I lie to you?

21
00:04:15,200 --> 00:04:17,600
Let me ignite you

22
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:20,100
When thunder crashes down

23
00:04:20,100 --> 00:04:24,300
When the world caves under my pressure

24
00:04:24,300 --> 00:04:27,700
There'll be no one to save

25
00:04:27,700 --> 00:04:32,400
Where is your pride, your human will to survive?

26
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:34,100
Was it just empty words...

27
00:04:34,100 --> 00:04:35,800
...for your grave?

28
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:38,200
I reach inside this soul

29
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:40,600
Now all that remains

30
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:44,200
Is delusion and decay

31
00:04:45,300 --> 00:04:48,000
Cuz of you, I live...

32
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:51,000
...this way!

33
00:04:51,500 --> 00:04:53,500
We're not rivals

34
00:04:53,500 --> 00:04:55,900
We're not equals

35
00:04:55,900 --> 00:04:58,300
We're not rivals

36
00:04:58,300 --> 00:05:01,000
We're not equals!

37
00:05:00,488 --> 00:05:02,588
Lightning never strikes twice in the same spot

38
00:05:02,588 --> 00:05:04,688
So go ahead and run up on me till you get your shot

39
00:05:04,688 --> 00:05:06,888
I see the weapon that you're hiding, come on ready or not

40
00:05:06,888 --> 00:05:09,388
Another life and you would never give a second thought

41
00:05:13,688 --> 00:05:16,288
Thinkin' your pride's different than mine

42
00:05:16,288 --> 00:05:18,988
Ticking all your vital signs off

43
00:05:21,088 --> 00:05:24,888
But we still gotta protect all our friends from our enemies

44
00:05:24,888 --> 00:05:26,988
Wouldn't you agree?

45
00:05:26,988 --> 00:05:30,788
Forged in fires of hell, god can't betray you

46
00:05:30,788 --> 00:05:35,088
If I'm a fallen angel, what does that make you?

47
00:05:35,088 --> 00:05:39,588
I'm not debasing myself to see the same view

48
00:05:39,588 --> 00:05:45,788
When it's your pride on the line, no one can save you from mine

49
00:05:45,788 --> 00:05:48,788
We're not rivals!

50
00:05:48,788 --> 00:05:51,288
We're not equals!

51
00:05:51,288 --> 00:05:53,488
We're not rivals!

52
00:05:53,488 --> 00:05:56,988
We're not equals!

53
00:06:01,788 --> 00:06:03,888
ハロー、みなさん！
Hello, everyone!

54
00:06:03,888 --> 00:06:05,588
Yeah yeah!

55
00:06:05,588 --> 00:06:07,988
Woo! This is... well thank... thank you!

56
00:06:07,988 --> 00:06:11,888
森カリオペです！Thank you so much everybody for coming to my birthday live!
This is Mori Calliope! Thank you so much everyone for coming to my birthday live!

57
00:06:11,888 --> 00:06:13,988
Here's the hashtag!

58
00:06:13,988 --> 00:06:17,988
UncutRock, right here, right here, right here!

59
00:06:17,988 --> 00:06:20,588
Check it out, everybody!

60
00:06:20,588 --> 00:06:24,488
Today's theme is obviously birthday, right?

61
00:06:24,488 --> 00:06:26,188
It's my birthday, and so...

62
00:06:26,188 --> 00:06:28,888
If you look behind us, we've got stones!

63
00:06:28,888 --> 00:06:30,588
Oh my gosh!

64
00:06:30,588 --> 00:06:34,988
What kind of stones, I wonder? Maybe birthday stones?

65
00:06:34,988 --> 00:06:37,788
Depending on the guest, I suppose. Mori Calliope's is diamond.

66
00:06:37,788 --> 00:06:39,588
So...

67
00:06:39,588 --> 00:06:41,588
Of course, you will see white behind me.

68
00:06:41,588 --> 00:06:45,788
Yes, and the idea is to sing original songs with guests,

69
00:06:45,788 --> 00:06:47,788
and also my own songs. And...

70
00:06:47,788 --> 00:06:50,388
I'm looking at the comments right now. Now, the show is in very high quality, so

71
00:06:50,388 --> 00:06:52,788
there's like a pretty big lag, but I'm looking. Woo, woo!

72
00:06:52,788 --> 00:06:54,488
There's a lot of clapping.

73
00:06:54,488 --> 00:06:56,588
Holy cannoli!

74
00:06:56,588 --> 00:06:58,688
Holy cannoli is right! こんばんは、こんばんは！
Holy cannoli is right! Good evening, good evening!

75
00:06:58,688 --> 00:07:01,088
コメント見てます！
I'm reading the comments!

76
00:07:01,088 --> 00:07:04,588
わあ、すごい！Happy birthday, happy birthday! Happy birthday wish, ありがとうございます！
Wow, amazing! Happy birthday, happy birthday! Thank you so much for the birthday wishes!

77
00:07:04,588 --> 00:07:07,288
And you know what, behind me is not only stones,

78
00:07:07,288 --> 00:07:10,388
