79
00:07:13,588 --> 00:07:15,788
Yes, that's right! Live band.

80
00:07:15,788 --> 00:07:17,788
Thank you so much to the band for coming.

81
00:07:17,788 --> 00:07:19,888
Now, in particular,

82
00:07:19,888 --> 00:07:22,988
