83
00:07:22,988 --> 00:07:24,888
Today, Park-san is here with us!

84
00:07:24,888 --> 00:07:26,988
カリちゃん、ハッピーバースデー。
Calli-chan, happy birthday.

85
00:07:26,988 --> 00:07:28,188
Thank you!

86
00:07:28,188 --> 00:07:29,388
今日はよろしくお願いします。
I look forward to working with you today.

87
00:07:29,388 --> 00:07:30,688
よろしくお願いします！
I look forward to working with you, too!

88
00:07:30,688 --> 00:07:33,688
Park-san is one of my favorite bass players ever.

89
00:07:33,688 --> 00:07:35,788
